law.text: Notwithstanding any provision of law to the contrary, the provisions of KRS Chapter 342 shall not apply to the provision of any service under KRS 205.5606 between the provider and the state or any state agency or political subdivision, the provider and the consumer, or as arranged by the provider and any fiscal intermediary, representative, or service advisor.
law.history: Created 2004 Ky. Acts ch. 60, sec. 3, effective July 13, 2004.
